Phase 1 (Basic Loop Test) - Success if:
- Detection probability > 0.9 for signals > 1 μT at 10cm
- False alarm rate < 0.01
- Response time < 500ms
- System runs for 24 hours without failure

Phase 2 (Enhanced Test) - Success if:
- Sensitivity < 10 nT/√Hz
- Detection probability > 0.95 for signals > 100 nT at 1m
- False alarm rate < 0.001
- Response time < 100ms
- Multi-sensor fusion improves performance by >20%

Phase 3 (Field Test) - Success if:
- Detect small drone (30cm) at >50m range
- Classification accuracy > 90%
- System operates in real environmental conditions
- Meets all safety and regulatory requirements
